did.unittitle: Yale University Library name/title card catalog

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

langmaterial.language: The materials are primarily in English, however many other languages are also represented.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The materials consist of the Yale University Library name/title catalog cards, which were retrospectively converted to electronic format.

altformavail.head: Existence and Location of Copies
altformavail.p: The entire name/title catalog is available via ORBIS, the Yale University Library online public access catalog (OPAC).

relatedmaterial.head: Related Materials
relatedmaterial.p: Related materials: Yale University Library Subject Card Catalog (RU 982).

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Cards were previously housed in the nave of the Sterling Memorial Library and rehoused from the card catalog cabinets to card file boxes. The first card in each box is listed. Filing errors from the original sequence were not corrected. Minor, non-critical inconsistencies may exist in the particular manner in which cards are described.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: Transferred from the Yale University Library, 2012.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Copyright for materials authored or otherwise produced as official business of Yale University is retained by Yale University. Copyright status for other collection materials is unknown. Transmission or reproduction of materials protected by U.S. Copyright Law (Title 17, U.S.C.) beyond that allowed by fair use requires the written permission of the copyright owners. Works not in the public domain cannot be commercially exploited without permission of the copyright owners. Responsibility for any use rests exclusively with the user.

odd.head: General
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 32-C (YRG 32-C), Records of Yale University Library departments and offices.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Yale University Library Name/Title Card Catalog (RU 1120). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The materials are arranged alphabetically by name and title.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.
